<h2>Update 1315G # Date 24 June 1998</h2>
<p>Chapter 49 - ADVANCE PAYMENTS - Advance payments extended to youth allowance and AUSTUDY payment. See guidelines 49.000 to 49.500.</p>
<p>Advance payments extended to youth allowance and AUSTUDY payment. Students will be able to have income support for three months waived so that this advance can cover educational expenses.</p>
<h2>Update 1314G # Date 24 June 1998</h2>
<p>Chapter 42 - PORTABILITY AND COMPARABLE FOREIGN PAYMENTS - Removal of overseas child payment to students 16 and over. See guidelines 42.400 to 42.425.</p>
