<p>Removal of qualification for sickness allowance for claimants under 16 as sickness allowance for U21s has been replaced by youth allowance. Insertion of study as qualifying for sickness allowance for students U21.</p>
<h2>Update 1288G # Date 24 June 1998</h2>
