<h2>Update 1130G # Date 15 January 1998</h2>
<p>Chapter 10 - WIDOWED PERSON ALLOWANCE - Widowed person allowance renamed bereavement allowance. See guidelines 10.000 to 10.2000.</p>
<p>From 1 January 1995, widowed person allowance was renamed bereavement allowance. This name change was implemented to avoid any confusion between widowed person allowance and widow allowance, which was introduced from 1 January 1995. This guide amendment replaces all references to widowed person allowance in Chapter 10 with bereavement allowance.</p>
